      <title>美国码头工人暂停罢工，亚洲航运股暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/shipping-shares-in-asia-tumble-after-us-dockworkers-pause-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸港口的码头工人同意暂停罢工后，亚洲各地的航运类股票暴跌，抑制了集装箱运费将因供应减少而上涨的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/shipping-shares-in-asia-tumble-after-us-dockworkers-pause-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 01:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
